<function>

access:   public

name: buildSelect

param: array, $parts

return: string

</function>

Build an SQL SELECT command string from its component parts.

* Parameters:

 * array //$parts//: The parts of the SELECT statement, generally from a Solar_Sql_Select object.

* Returns string: An SQL SELECT command string.

We use this so that drivers can append or wrap with LIMIT
clauses or emulation.